{"tid":1810406,"cid":5,"subCid":10,"title":"政府因應武漢不明肺炎啟動嚴重應變級別","createTime":"2020-01-04T00:18:05.000Z","updateTime":"2020-01-04T00:40:50.000Z","uid":41343,"like":3,"dislike":2,"uniUserReply":4,"replies":[{"pid":"f9add48f5b275b5b85ba897464f752489607ae1c","tid":1810406,"uid":41343,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2020-01-04T00:18:05.000Z","msg":"因應武漢出現不明原因的病毒性肺炎感染病例，政府作出風險評估後，公佈啟動應變計劃，並即時將應變級別由「戒備」升至「嚴重」。<br />\n<br />\n衞生防護中心發言人說，在嚴重應變級別下，現時武漢出現的病毒性肺炎病例群組個案，可被視為一種「對公共衞生有重要性的新型傳染病」，指不知道能令人類致病的病原體所引致的任何傳染病，但由於特性或已改變，因此不論是否具備在人與人之間有效地傳播的能力，人類亦會受到感染。<br />\n<br />\n發言人說，有關疾病現時對市民健康即時影響屬於中等，政府會因應最新的科研實證和發展，不時評估風險，啟動或解除應變級別，並採取相應的防控措施。<br />\n<br />\n<a href=\"https://news.rthk.hk/rthk/ch/component/k2/1500952-20200104.htm\" data-sr-url=\"https://r.lihkg.com/link?u=https%3A%2F%2Fnews.rthk.hk%2Frthk%2Fch%2Fcomponent%2Fk2%2F1500952-20200104.htm&d=GO0vWKcqTLT5bpzdAOrPDs5RZDHrhPshgzcG8Nqr5vw%3D&h=7d3f0210\" data-ef-url=\"https://embed.lih.kg/frame?u=https%3A%2F%2Fnews.rthk.hk%2Frthk%2Fch%2Fcomponent%2Fk2%2F1500952-20200104.htm&h=99c0af88\" target=\"_blank\">https://news.rthk.hk/rthk/ch/component/k2/1500952-20200104.htm</a>"},{"pid":"8c3262735c39c00dae21037cfdd7c85ae8b716a3","tid":1810406,"uid":149342,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2020-01-04T00:19:01.000Z","msg":"雞始好野"},{"pid":"525b4130daf1bd618ee9b0c2d9909e27ee6398bf","tid":1810406,"uid":249705,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2020-01-04T00:19:46.000Z","msg":"Push"},{"pid":"ca9f20deeff7d395794eb59c9e8bf11063020b23","tid":1810406,"uid":249705,"like":3,"dislike":0,"score":3,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2020-01-04T00:23:27.000Z","msg":"戴普通外科口罩/N95<br />\n公共地方唔好周圍摸<br />\n洗多啲手 帶消毒酒精<br />\n做運動強身健體 順便練埋體能<br />\n<br />\n<span style=\"color: red;\"><span style=\"font-size: x-large;\">唔死先可以做世界冠軍</span></span>"},{"pid":"5d29338d35c209bb7dfd1386d10f960bda73b80b","tid":1810406,"uid":302944,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2020-01-04T00:40:50.000Z"